Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to present a rare opportunity to secure a modern industrial unit in Eastern Creek, featuring:

-	3,307.7sqm* warehouse/office space
-	Includes modern office accommodation 
-	Access via 3 on grade roller doors and a loading dock 
-	Internal clearance up to twelve (12) metres 
-	Very generous hardstand provides simplistic access for large vehicles
-	LED lighting throughout warehouse, as well as ample natural light
-	Racking and modern office fit out may remain (subject to negotiations)
-	Sub-lease or Assignment of Lease available 

Contact exclusive agent John Micallef for further details.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: 3,307.7SQM IN EASTERN CREEK WITH A DOCK!

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Unit 3, 2 Southridge Street is an excellent and well designed facility located in one of the most sought after locations in Western Sydney.

Key features include:

- 4,503sqm office/warehouse  
- Situated at M7 Business Hub, Eastern Creek
- Excellent access to the M4/M2 Motorway and Westlink M7 
- Excellent exposure to old Wallgrove Road
- High clearance warehouse space up to 12.1m
- Excellent quality office accomodation
- Access via six (6) roller shutter doors and one (1) dock 
- Quality amenities
- Large awning over doors and docks

For further information, please call the listed agents.

CBRE has the pleasure of presenting an opportunity to secure one of the few remaining parcels of vacant industrial land in the ever popular Eastern Creek Industrial precinct, offering:

- 5,381sqm prime industrial land
- Fully secured and serviced site
- Includes a 2,657sqm building which is half completed
- Site benefits from significant exposure to passing traffic on the M4 Motorway
- Flexible IN1 – General Industrial zoning allowing for a wide range of users (STCA)
- Opportunity to acquire land within an established and well sought after precinct
- Excellent access to the Great Western Highway, M4 & M7 Motorways
- The property will be sold via Auction which will be held on-site on Tuesday 13th October 2020 at 2.30PM (AEST).

For a copy of the Contract for Sale, the Information Memorandum, or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusively listed agents.
